column16: Albert Pujols pops out to shortstop Reid Brignac.
Josh Hamilton walks.   Peter Bourjos to 3rd.    Mike Trout to 2nd.
Mike Trout singles on a line drive to center fielder Brett Gardner.   Chris Iannetta scores.    Peter Bourjos to 2nd.
Peter Bourjos reaches on a fielder's choice out, second baseman David Adams to catcher Austin Romine.   Alberto Callaspo out at home.    Chris Iannetta to 3rd.
Erick Aybar strikes out swinging.   Chris Iannetta to 2nd.
Chris Iannetta singles on a ground ball to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.   Alberto Callaspo to 3rd.
